metadata.description:
Although the workload increases sharply, Zheng Xun orders his subordinates not to miss even a little seemingly useless information.



He is more aware of the seriousness of the incident than most people. It has shaken not only the national foundation but also the national foundation.



He did not know the reason behind it, and he could only hope that this method of finding a needle in a haystack would not miss any clues that might come up.



He looked it up, opening and closing it.
